&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Have proficiency in tax provision software (OneSource Tax Provision, CoreTax, or similar) and various ERP systems&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Excel at managing multiple workstreams and coordinating complex operational processes&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Thrive in fast-paced, scrappy, and dynamic environments and can adapt quickly to evolving needs&lt;/p&gt;
